# Yehuda Huri — Personal portfolio

Personal portfolio / showcase site for **Yehuda Huri** — Senior Full Stack Engineer & System
Designer at Amdocs. Public pages present experience, skills, and shipped products, and let
visitors get in touch. This is a **frontend-only marketing site** — no backend, auth, or database.

## Stack (do not relitigate without explicit user request)

- Frontend: **React 19 + Vite + TypeScript**, **MUI v6** (theme + `sx`),
  **React Router v7**, **react-i18next** (en + he, RTL).
- No backend, no Firebase, no Redux, no contact form — visitors reach out via social links.
- Path alias `@` → `frontend/src` when configured in Vite.

## Design authority

- **UI/UX Pro Max** skill (`.cursor/skills/ui-ux-pro-max`) is the primary guide for layout,
  typography, color, landing patterns, and UX checklist.
- Persist approved choices to `design-system/yehuda-huri/MASTER.md` when a direction is locked.
- Style with **MUI theme tokens** — extend `frontend/src/theme/` (presets + `DemoThemeColors.ts`),
  not raw hex in components. Default preset: **`fullstackForge`** (blue accent, `#2563EB`).
- Marketing pages live under `frontend/src/pages/marketing/` inside `AppLayout`.

## Core conventions

- All user-facing copy is **i18n** (`frontend/src/config/locales/en.json` + `he.json`).
- **Reuse first** — shared consts, utils, hooks; see scoped rules below.
- Both **light and dark** modes must remain fully usable after any visual change.
- **Accuracy:** never claim skills/experience Yehuda hasn't confirmed (no iOS-native, Unity,
  Firebase, "20+ years", or specific telco client names).

## Scoped rules (auto-attach by glob)

- `10-no-magic-values.mdc`, `20-dry-reuse.mdc`, `30-theme-tokens.mdc`, `40-i18n.mdc`,
  `50-structure-and-naming.mdc`, `60-marketing-redesign.mdc`, `70-marketing-product.mdc`.

